{"tid":1544930,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"我間中 撚下狗 很喜歡自由","createTime":"2019-09-05T17:23:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T04:21:10.000Z","uid":264950,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e904ce6a1403e47097c17b1798ed9616f6645fdd","tid":1544930,"uid":264950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:23:36.000Z","msg":"曾話過 怕跌底 但總要自救"},{"pid":"cc617a22bbee3d404474bacc30245a7c3509eccd","tid":1544930,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:23:47.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"73600f68f63ed058197ecf6094402747031bb1df","tid":1544930,"uid":251292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:25:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"515386c73463937f36b34739e56714c1c7b6aa19","tid":1544930,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:25:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">撤LLM 對準政權</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNutjAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNutjAi.jpg&h=1817afe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">得到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 全民反共 對準政權！</span></span></strong><br />\n黑警、黨鐵，港共全部都係人民既敵人<br />\n而背後一直有一個終極大Boss中共<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻中共絕對係十個煲得兩個蓋，準備爆煲。<br />\n今日唔號召世界圍堵中共，更待何時？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用#Chinazi黎connect全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. Connect所有黃絲。</span></strong><br />\n殘酷既現實係，並唔係所有黃絲都支持勇武。但黃絲最驚就係共產黨打到黎，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bb06a4ef374831712500804b034d53229cea5ee5","tid":1544930,"uid":183898,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:26:45.000Z","msg":"面對黑警狠咬 大眾逼於接受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7134a432122fb42ec20a35f9bfd07d9562a317de","tid":1544930,"uid":53003,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:26:55.000Z","msg":"遇過popo 的損友"},{"pid":"02a5cbc0e467f63ee623cf9e585826c9ad5356b4","tid":1544930,"uid":178918,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"bb06a4ef374831712500804b034d53229cea5ee5","tid":1544930,"uid":183898,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:26:45.000Z","msg":"面對黑警狠咬 大眾逼於接受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:47:03.000Z","msg":"面對黑警狠<span style=\"color: red;\">狠</span>咬 大眾逼於接受<br />\n亦試過當狗咁撚"},{"pid":"62a43a4bec56f02c5636c3d72156a0a37f41f479","tid":1544930,"uid":264950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02a5cbc0e467f63ee623cf9e585826c9ad5356b4","tid":1544930,"uid":178918,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"bb06a4ef374831712500804b034d53229cea5ee5","tid":1544930,"uid":183898,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:26:45.000Z","msg":"面對黑警狠咬 大眾逼於接受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:47:03.000Z","msg":"面對黑警狠<span style=\"color: red;\">狠</span>咬 大眾逼於接受<br />\n亦試過當狗咁撚"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:56:40.000Z","msg":"亦試過當狗咁撚個key點唱？<br />\nbtw<br />\n去上街 只會忍 黑警沖上前"},{"pid":"036699903125c9d2558f8af7cd6e381eb0d6c79d","tid":1544930,"uid":36677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62a43a4bec56f02c5636c3d72156a0a37f41f479","tid":1544930,"uid":264950